Info
--------------
Basic map in which the player travels through teleporters to specific rooms in the map. There are 13 small rooms.
--------------

Each team has a buy zone.

Room 1 and 2 are spawns.

20 players per team


IMPORTANT
--------------
Room 8 has has sound. Please add your own song in "sounds/fy_teleporters/sabh.mp3"
MP3 is not included.
